replies.body:
I know this is out of context of the thread, but...
I really want the backgrounds from the runes reforged system as posters (they're absolutely gorgeus, really love the landscaping and the mood, atmosphere), but I can't find them anywhere. {{sticker:sg-janna}} 

Could you maybe ask the art team to release them in a good quality for me to admire? 
I would like to have them without the rune system over it, with only the landscape/background. 

The only one I could find that is like this, is precision:

https://lolstatic-a.akamaihd.net/frontpage/apps/prod/preseason-2018/en_US/a6708b7ae3dbc0b25463f9c8e259a513d2c4c7e6/assets/img/runeBuilder/assets/construct/8000/environment.png    {{sticker:sg-jinx}}

Just wanna say that I'm having serious issues using the new rune pages in champ select because I have a low end machine. The entire client feels extra slow since the update.

Secondly, can you guys please add an option to reset points like the last mastery system? When I went to delete the page (i.e. reset it so I could put new runes in) I got kicked off the page and had to start a slow process of trying to pick them out again. When the game started I was using a premade page instead. It's frustrating as hell.

{{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}}
